thread_mc_data_manipulate_lib_hao_1
===================================

The c++ matrix library, calculate mean value and error bar, and write them into files.


============================================================
For single thread, only write the mean value to file.

============================================================
For multi-thread, write gloal mean, local mean and error bar
to file.

Global mean value:
( \sum_thread {denominator} ) / ( \sum_thread {numerator} )

Thread mean value is
1/thread_number* ( \sum_thread { denominator/numerator } )

Error bar is from thread mean values
============================================================



Dependence on 0 level lib_hao:
1. mpi_lib_hao_0
2. kahan_error_analysis_lib_hao_0 
3. tensor_lib_hao_0

